## Task 2 — Archived Company Website

### Technique: Wayback Machine

The company claims to have been founded in 2025, but a former employee says it existed long before. To verify, we searched for the site's first snapshot on the Wayback Machine.

URL provided in the challenge: `warc-acme.com/jef/`

```
https://web.archive.org/web/*/warc-acme.com
```

The earliest recorded snapshot revealed the original publication date of the site.

**Flag:** `THM{20160210224602}`

