## Tools Used

| Tool | Purpose |
|---|---|
| exiftool | EXIF and GPS metadata extraction |
| Wayback Machine | Website publication history verification |
| Google Maps | GPS coordinate geolocation |
| unzip / cat | ODT file extraction and analysis |
| Sherlock | Username search across public platforms |

```bash
# Extract image metadata
exiftool photo.jpg

# Extract ODT contents
unzip document.odt -d output_folder/
cat output_folder/meta.xml

# Username search
sherlock markwilliams7243
```
